---
title: Double Caribbean Chicken Strips & Coconut Sauce with Charred Pineapple Slaw & Crushed Peanuts
description: Eat the tropical rainbow tonight with this vibrant collection of veggies and chicken strips cooked in our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning. We’re keeping those beach vibes going by adding a charred pineapple slaw, coconut sauce and a hint of nutty peanuts.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/654c757f02458a46e49a8920-8a543681.jpeg
